SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed * distance_traveled AS fuel_efficiency FROM fuel_consumption_data WHERE distance_traveled BETWEEN 50 AND 200;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT fuel_type) AS distinct_fuel_types FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT * FROM fuel_consumption_data WHERE vehicle_id IN (1,3,5);
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, CASE WHEN distance_traveled > 100 THEN 'High Mileage' ELSE 'Low Mileage' END AS mileage_category FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY fuel_type) AS row_num FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY fuel_type ORDER BY fuel_consumed DESC) AS fuel_consumed_rank FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, LAG(fuel_consumed) OVER(ORDER BY vehicle_id) AS prev_fuel_consumption FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, LEAD(distance_traveled) OVER(ORDER BY vehicle_id) AS next_distance_traveled FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, NTILE(2) OVER(ORDER BY fuel_consumed) AS fuel_consumed_ntile FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT DISTINCT fuel_type, AVG(fuel_consumed) OVER(PARTITION BY fuel_type) AS avg_fuel_consumed FROM fuel_consumption_data;

SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, FIRST_VALUE(distance_traveled) OVER(PARTITION BY fuel_type ORDER BY distance_traveled) AS first_distance_traveled FROM fuel_consumption_data;

SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, LAST_VALUE(fuel_consumed) OVER(ORDER BY vehicle_id ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND UNBOUNDED FOLLOWING) AS last_fuel_consumed FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, NTILE(3) OVER(ORDER BY vehicle_id) AS vehicle_id_ntile FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, PERCENT_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY fuel_consumed) AS fuel_consumed_percent_rank FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, CUME_DIST() OVER(PARTITION BY fuel_type ORDER BY fuel_consumed) AS fuel_consumed_cume_dist FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, DENSE_RANK() OVER(ORDER BY vehicle_id) AS vehicle_id_dense_rank FROM fuel_consumption_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, fuel_type, fuel_consumed, distance_traveled, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY fuel_type ORDER BY distance_traveled DESC) AS row_num_desc FROM fuel_consumption_data;

SELECT fc.vehicle_id, vp.top_speed, vd.engine_size FROM fuel_consumption_data fc JOIN vehicle_performance vp ON fc.vehicle_id = vp.vehicle_id JOIN vehicle_details vd ON fc.vehicle_id = vd.vehicle_id WHERE vd.engine_size > 2.0;

SELECT di.driver_name, di.age, vd.make, fc.fuel_efficiency FROM driver_info di JOIN vehicle_details vd ON di.vehicle_id = vd.vehicle_id JOIN fuel_consumption_data fc ON di.vehicle_id = fc.vehicle_id WHERE di.age > 30;

SELECT vd.make, vp.top_speed, fc.fuel_consumed / fc.trip_distance AS mileage_per_km FROM vehicle_details vd JOIN vehicle_performance vp ON vd.vehicle_id = vp.vehicle_id JOIN fuel_consumption_data fc ON vd.vehicle_id = fc.vehicle_id WHERE mileage_per_km > 0.08;

SELECT di.driver_name, vd.make, fc.fuel_type, fc.fuel_consumed FROM driver_info di JOIN vehicle_details vd ON di.vehicle_id = vd.vehicle_id JOIN fuel_consumption_data fc ON vd.vehicle_id = fc.vehicle_id WHERE fc.fuel_consumed > 50;

SELECT vd.make, vp.top_speed, di.driver_name, di.age FROM vehicle_details vd JOIN vehicle_performance vp ON vd.vehicle_id = vp.vehicle_id JOIN driver_info di ON vd.vehicle_id = di.vehicle_id WHERE di.age < 40;
